OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777507377
OL,3,CVideo shows alleged attacker moments
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green stabbing
OL,6,FITV News has obtained footage showing
OL,7,Fthe Golders Green stabbing suspect
OL,8,Fappearing to chase a man moments after
OL,9,Fthe attack.
OL,11,FThe footage shows the suspect, wearing
OL,12,Fgrey trousers and a navy jacket, with
OL,13,Fa beige rucksack on his back. He
OL,14,Fappears to follow a man around a
OL,15,Fparked vehicle.
OL,17,FTwo Jewish men were stabbed in Golders
OL,18,FGreen on Wednesday morning, and the
OL,19,Fincident has since been declared a
OL,20,Fterrorist attack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
