OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777507377
OL,3,CVideo shows alleged attacker moments
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green stabbing
OL,6,FIsaac Cohen, who was an eyewitness,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News: "We tried to save
OL,8,Fpeople."
OL,10,FA 45-year-old man has been arrested in
OL,11,FGolders Green in connection with the
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,FThe two victims, one in his 70s and
OL,15,Fthe other in his 30s, are in a stable
OL,16,Fcondition in hospital following the
OL,17,Fattack, which happened shortly after
OL,18,F11am in Highfield Avenue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
