OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777507377
OL,3,CVideo shows alleged attacker moments
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green stabbing
OL,6,FThe suspect was armed with a knife and
OL,7,F"attempting to stab Jewish members of
OL,8,Fthe public", Jewish security group
OL,9,FShomrim said on social media.
OL,11,FHe also tried to stab police officers
OL,12,Fwhen he was stopped, and was tasered
OL,13,Fbefore being arrested, the Met Police
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
