OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1777507377
OL,3,CVideo shows alleged attacker moments
OL,4,Cafter Golders Green stabbing
OL,6,FThe attack prompted calls for action
OL,7,Ffrom the Chief Rabbi and the Israeli
OL,8,Fforeign ministry, following a series
OL,9,Fof incidents targeting Jewish sites in
OL,10,FLondon.
OL,12,FChief Rabbi Sir Ephraim Mirvis said
OL,13,F"words of condemnation are no longer
OL,14,Fsufficient" and called for "meaningful
OL,15,Faction".
OL,17,FThe scene is around half a mile from a
OL,18,Fmemorial wall where an attempted arson
OL,19,Fattack took place on Monday, and near
OL,20,Fwhere four Jewish community ambulances
OL,21,Fwere destroyed by fire in late March.
